text:
Hi, is there a popular free or paid collection of HubSpot email modules and sections that anyone can recommend? I'm looking for banners, buttons, cards, blockquotes, etc.
My goal is to combine the HubSpot cms-theme-boilerplate with a collection of premade email modules and sections in order to get a head start on creating email templates.

<https://inboundelements.com/HubSpot-templates/elements-HubSpot-email-templates/|https://inboundelements.com/HubSpot-templates/elements-HubSpot-email-templates/> have never used them but like the collection
